title: Striking aerial view of Birmingham New Street and city's skyline from Rotunda
text:
Play video As part of ITV News Central's coverage of the opening of Birmingham New Street station, we're at the top of the rotunda getting some aerial views.
Here's a striking view of trains entering the station - from a rather unusual angle.
